title: Match of the Day - 8th November 2014 - 720p50 X264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD  
Date: Saturday 8th November 2014 
Time: 23:00 to 00:20

Gary Lineker presents highlights from all of the day's Premier League fixtures. On paper the biggest fixture looked to be Chelsea's visit to Liverpool. The Blues' 2-0 victory at Anfield last season ended Liverpool's 11-match winning streak and spelled the beginning of the end for the Reds' title hopes. So far this season it has been the London side who have looked the more likely champions but there is still a long way to go. Other fixtures included Manchester United hosting Crystal Palace at Old Trafford, last season's champions Manchester City visiting QPR and Burnley and Hull meeting at Turf Moor. Southampton welcomed Leicester to St Mary's while there was a battle of the claret and blues when West Ham and Aston Villa met at Upton Park.
